Tic-Tac-Toe Game.

Features to implement:
  Functional tic tac toe game.
  The ability to sign up, sign in and sign out. 
  The ability to challenge either the computer or fellow users to a match. 
  To be able to send an alert to a user if someone has challeneged them to a game or if someone has played a move.
  To be able to store moves played on the database so that a user can sign in and view and resume incomplete matches.
  The ability for a user to view all of their scores through their profile page.
  Restricting access to games to the user logged on to play.
  Restricting access to the tic tac toe game unless a player has signed up.